Powers.DescShort: Auto Res Fear, Smashing, Lethal, Fire, Cold, Toxic
Powers.DescLong: Ember Demons are resistant to Fear effects.  They are also resistant to Lethal, Smashing, Fire, Cold and Toxic damage.  They can also use Fire Blast and Shield of Hellfire.

Powers.DescShort: Auto PBAoE, Owner +Res(Fire, Lethal, Smash, Cold, Toxic)
Powers.DescLong: The Ember Demon's Ember Shield grants an additional damage resistance to Lethal, Smashing, Toxic, Cold and Fire damage bonus to its owner.
Sends a Blast of Fire at a targeted foe and sets the target on fire for a short period of time. Slower recharge rate than Flares, but more damage. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Fast

Powers.DescShort: Auto PBAoE, Ally +Res(Fire, Lethal, Smash, Cold, Toxic)
Powers.DescLong: The Ember Demon bathes your allies in an Ember Shield increasing their damage resistance to Lethal, Smashing, Toxic, Cold and Fire damage.
